main event: A civilian reported a UFO observation in Enon, Ohio on June 10, 1967.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 10 seconds., The object was visualized from the ground., The color of the object was described as white., The observer noted the object was silent., The conclusion of the report stated there was insufficient data for evaluation.
witness description: The witness is a minor who provided a vague account of the event.
